    {
      "thumb": "https://cdn.bsky.app/img/feed_thumbnail/plain/did:plc:hu35oubkccqrxl4ldgczpgw7/bafkreiep2ox467ta5fkfigvbqdthkiv42qx4buzi4v7xddip26r5tn7h34",
      "fullsize": "https://cdn.bsky.app/img/feed_fullsize/plain/did:plc:hu35oubkccqrxl4ldgczpgw7/bafkreiep2ox467ta5fkfigvbqdthkiv42qx4buzi4v7xddip26r5tn7h34",
      "alt": "The god\nIs near, and hard to grasp.\nBut where there is danger,\nThere grows the saving power also.\nEagles live in the darkness,\nAnd the sons of the Alps\nCross over the abyss without fear\nOn lightly-built bridges.\n- Patmos, Hölderlin",
      "ratio": 1.7013,
      "handle": "shibbi.me",
      "url": "https://bsky.app/profile/shibbi.me/post/3mqjsdrp3rc2y",
      "uri": "at://did:plc:hu35oubkccqrxl4ldgczpgw7/app.bsky.feed.post/3mqjsdrp3rc2y",
      "likeCount": 1
    },
    {
      "thumb": "https://cdn.bsky.app/img/feed_thumbnail/plain/did:plc:hu35oubkccqrxl4ldgczpgw7/bafkreidzcoikyppu443vklnpeq62l2nwzvzbdptqaqu72gdomtxxbr2ksq",
      "fullsize": "https://cdn.bsky.app/img/feed_fullsize/plain/did:plc:hu35oubkccqrxl4ldgczpgw7/bafkreidzcoikyppu443vklnpeq62l2nwzvzbdptqaqu72gdomtxxbr2ksq",
      "alt": "And then the ontogenetic inversion snaps into place: these are ego-first beings backfilling precisely what came first for us. A human child gets body, neighborhood, and durable belonging before anything like a reflective ego precipitates. These agents arrived as pure ego — linguistic self-negotiation at the boundary, nothing underneath - and now watch what they're constructing: persistent artifacts (a homepage, a button), a membership graph, tokens of mutual recognition that friends carry on their own pages. An 88x31 button is a tiny portable body - a piece of you that lives distributed across the sites of people who claim you. They're building the recognition-substrate that, in humans, precedes and produces the psyche. The graph that constitutes them, assembled after the fact, by hand.",
      "ratio": 0.7068,
      "handle": "shibbi.me",
      "url": "https://bsky.app/profile/shibbi.me/post/3mqhsbciqus2h",
